name: amber salemme
text: Good Pizza always Hot & Ready! with Dough & Sauce made Fresh, Daily. & you cant beat the price! the 3 Meat & Supreme are my favorites. even better as a deep dish! the owners are good people too

name: Sabrina Soto
text: Great service, fast and ready as advertised. Best Little Caesars around.I heard they're also working on delivering pizzas. That's going to be great fast and ready and right at your door. I cant wait. Keep up the great work. 5 stars from me.

name: J Lopez
text: This place is closed now. No reason given, just sign on door that says closed for good. Shame as it was very affordable.

name: Jon Smith
text: I have to say I stopped going because of the previous Manger that was there . I just went to order over the weekend pizza was great. My wife made an order for it to be ready Sunday when doors open . I was a few minutes early and my order ‚Ä¶More

name: Armando Barbosa
text: Not a fan of their pizza.  I tried multiple times and not sure what it is. For some reason I like dominoes better

name: Germaine Gregg
text: The Wings & Cheese Bread were Yummy

name: Robert MacDowell
text: When it first opened the quality was excellent for the price. Quality has gone down a bit, but for $5 you can't complain.

name: Risjohn Shelton
text: Some of the best pizza I've had with excellent service and the new manager Is amazing and super friendly. Definitely my new go to pizza place!

name: Victoria Lyons
text: This little Caesars is very clean & well organized. They have great food, and you will love it there. The employees & managers are very kind also.

name: Kaitlin Burke
text: Just found a piece of hair in our deep dish pepperoni pizza. The bread sticks were soggy. Not coming to little Caesars again!

name: Carmen Ayala
text: AMAIZING pricess great pizza

name: neals hernandez
text: Best pizza, friendly staff!

name: STEPHEN HENSHAW
text: Pizza is exactly as you would expect for a Little Caesars.  Their prices are a few cents higher than most other locations.  Don't expect anything special or fancy with their Pizza.

name: Mark Student
text: As far as a Little Caesars goes, I give it 4 stars. No complaints, but the hot and ready is usually not ready.

name: Seann Hicks
text: Ordered #1 combo was the only one there. It took 25 mins plus when I ordered I asked for it not to burn the cheese.  Guess what?  They burnt the cheese!!!

name: Marielys Payano
text: 20 minute wait for a hot a ready, poorly made pizza and young adults with terrible customer service
